Package: mojortemplate
Type: Package
Title: Minimal Mojo <-> R FFI Template
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Patrick", "Bair", email = "patrick@xyzhomework.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: A copy-this-to-start template for calling Mojo shared libraries
    from R via the C ABI. Demonstrates scalar exports, zero-copy buffers,
    SIMD reductions, host callbacks, and an ALTREP-backed numeric vector
    whose sum() dispatches directly to Mojo SIMD code.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
SystemRequirements: pixi (https://pixi.sh) and a Modular Mojo toolchain when
    built with MOJORTEMPLATE_BUILD=1. Without the env flag the package
    installs with a no-op fallback.
URL: https://github.com/xyz-homework/mojor-template
BugReports: https://github.com/xyz-homework/mojor-template/issues
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0), bench
Config/testthat/edition: 3
